<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc., bekennen etc., als uns die
                                <expan>hochwirdig<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> fürsten und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> zu Maincz, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ott zu
                        Tryer, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Dietreich zu Cöln, erczbischöffe,
                                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan>, <expan>pfallnczgr<ex>af</ex></expan> bey
                        Reyn, des <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> reichs ercztruchsesz und herczog in
                        Peyern, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> zu
                                <expan>Sachs<ex>en</ex></expan>, und <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>,
                        alle des <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs <expan>kurfürst<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        unsre gnedige <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hant, daz sie auf <app><note><q type="date">der
                            <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zwölfpott<ex>en</ex></expan> schydungtag</q>15.07.1422</note></app> nehst kombt mit iren selbs
                        leiben gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zu kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und daz sie auch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigiste<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künig und darczu <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und <expan>stette<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, alsdann auch gen
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>zu kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, und an uns
                            <expan>gesunne<ex>n</ex></expan> und begert hant, in geleyt zu  geben,
                        also geben wir den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>kurfürste<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> zu Maincz, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Otten
                        zu Tryer, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dietr<ex>ich</ex></expan> zu Cöln,
                            <expan>erczbischoff<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>pfallnczgr<ex>af</ex></expan> bey
                        Reyn, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> zu
                        Sachsen, und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc., und ir
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> grafen,
                        <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, reͣten, <expan>geistliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>w<ex>er</ex>ntlichen</expan>, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>knechte<ex>n</ex></expan>, dienern und den iren und
                                <expan>nemliche<ex>n</ex></expan> allen den, die sie samentlich
